---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Contact" description="Get in touch with Selcurate.">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-h1 font-bold font-heading text-foreground mb-6">Contact</h1>

    <div class="prose">
      <p>
        Have a question, feedback, or found an error in one of our guides?
        We'd love to hear from you.
      </p>

      <h2>Email</h2>
      <p>
        <a href="mailto:hello@selcurate.com">hello@selcurate.com</a>
      </p>
      <p>
        We aim to respond within 48 hours.
      </p>

      <h2>What We Can Help With</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Corrections or updates to product information</li>
        <li>Data removal requests (GDPR, PDPA)</li>
        <li>Affiliate partnership inquiries</li>
        <li>General feedback on our guides</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>What We Can't Help With</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Product support (contact the manufacturer directly)</li>
        <li>Order issues (contact the retailer where you purchased)</li>
        <li>Sponsored content requests (we don't accept paid placements)</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
